kg) \\u2022 Yahya Al Ghotany, taekwondo (-68kg) \\u2022 Mohammad Amin Alsalami, athletics (long jump) \\u2022 Amir Ansari, cycling (time trial) \\u2022 Sibghatullah Arab, judo (mixed team & -81kg) \\u2022 Mahboubeh Barbari Zharfi, judo (mixed team & +78kg) \\u2022 Edilio Francisco Centeno Nieves, shooting (10m air pistol) \\u2022 Muna Dahouk, judo (mixed team & -57kg) \\u2022 Jamal Abdelmaji Eisa Mohammed, athletics (10,000m) \\u2022 Saeid Fazloula, canoe (K-1 1,000m) \\u2022 Tachlowini Gabriyesos, athletics (marathon) \\u2022 Eyeru Gebru, cycling (road race) \\u2022 Yekta Jamali Galeh, weightlifting (-81kg) \\u2022 Fernando Dayan Jorge Enriquez, canoe (C-1 1,000m) \\u2022 Dorian Keletela, athletics (100m) \\u2022 Adnan Khankan, judo (mixed team & -100kg) \\u2022 Perina Lokure, athletics (800m) \\u2022 Iman Mahdavi, wrestling (freestyle -74kg) \\u2022 Alaa Maso, swimming (50m freestyle) \\u2022 Kasra Mehdipournejad, taekwondo (+80kg) \\u2022 Dina Pouryounes Langeroudi, taekwondo (-49kg) \\u2022 Mohammad Rashnonezhad, judo (mixed team & -60kg) \\u2022 Amir Rezanejad, canoe (canoe slalom) \\u2022 Nigara Shaheen, judo (mixed team & -63kg) \\u2022 Luna Solomon, shooting (10m air rifle) \\u2022 Saman Soltani, canoe (K-1 500m) \\u2022 Musa Suliman, athletics (800m) \\u2022 Manizha Talash, breaking (Bgirl) \\u2022 Hadi Tiranvalipour, taekwondo (-58kg) \\u2022 Jamal Valizadeh, wrestling (Greco-Roman -60kg) MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your